Who, what are you doing and with whom?
Where and why?
Do not share information (guesses) you have about the private lives of your colleagues with everyone!
Do not abuse your colleague's trust when he shares his most intimate secrets with you!
Bury in yourself what you have heard and do not gossip about your colleague in his absence, even though others also know his things.
You're taking sick leave without a reason?
