Jumps, laughs, phone calls
Are you in the middle of your work, but are you suddenly taken out of it by the ridicule of your colleagues?
Have you unwittingly overheard a telephone conversation that you would have been better off not overhearing?
Don't annoy your colleagues with your humming, singing, loud conversations (except when you do it above their heads), kicking, constant blasphemies, voicing your discontents out loud.
