You are not referring to the chaos that may be in the office, nor to the noise your colleagues make!
You must admit if you have made a mistake that harms others and you must make up for it!
Ask how you can make up for your mistake!
Do you feel too at home at the office?
Jogging shoes and slippers: very comfortable for the home, but not suitable for the office!
Don't wear a comfortable jogging suit even if your occupation allows it!
Don't be messy, respect your colleagues and yourself by wearing everyday, elegant and beautiful clothes when your occupation demands it!
